# Switch

> Tactile toggles with clear state color and movement.  
> **Status**: Beta


## Basic Usage
::TuffCodeBlock{lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TuffSwitch v-model="enabled" />
    <TuffSwitch v-model="enabled" size="small" />
  </template>
---
::

